attr.title: Vacuous Sugar Quest
attr.desc: Play as Vac, an adventurer trying to climb Sugar Mountain to prove her sugar gliding abilities!
attr.inst: Download the game from itch.io (https://walfie.itch.io/vacuous-sugar-quest), extract, and place VacuousSugarQuest.pck in this port's folder.
